<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[١٠٨ سورة الكوثر]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة الكوثر <span class="c2">(١٠٨)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٣]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِنَّا أَعْطَيْناكَ الْكَوْثَرَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَانْحَرْ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِنَّ شانِئَكَ هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١-<span class="c5"> إِنَّا أَعْطَيْناكَ الْكَوْثَرَ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>الْكَوْثَرَ الخير الكثير الدائم فى الدنيا والآخرة.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَانْحَرْ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَصَلِّ فدم على الصلاة لربك خالصة له.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَانْحَرْ ذبائحك شكرا له على ما أولاك من كرامة وخصك من خير.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> إِنَّ شانِئَكَ هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِنَّ شانِئَكَ مبغضك.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ المنقطع عن كل خير.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>